{"tid":1229598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《還原612警察戰略部署》","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T03:47:58.000Z","uid":84497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"265d882db7966db956b197c19f6d4c2f1d4bcf94","tid":1229598,"uid":84497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"1: 在鐵馬前雙方對侍，警察不能前進，也不能跨過鐵馬拘捕示威者。因此設立了鐵馬前的防線A。警方知道，警員一旦跨過鐵馬，他們就會夾在人群和鐵馬之間，成了甕中之鱉。因此堅守不出。<br />\n<br />\n2: 到達適當時機，全隊退後，設立防線B，騰出了A和B之間的空地，引示威者上前。此刻，示威者就夾在警察防線和鐵馬之間，倒成了甕中之鱉。<br />\n<br />\n3: 由於這批示威者實際上是過了先前設立的防線A，故此，警方就能以「穿越警察防線」及「逼使警方在退無可退的情況下」為由，出師有名地使用暴力摳打，射擊，拘捕夾在中間的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n4: 警察立即蜂擁而出， 趁後面的示威者還正在慢慢跨越鐵馬，甚至卡在了鐵馬之際，在空地追擊為數不多被夾在了防線前的示威者。這批示威者無險可守，後無退路。<br />\n<br />\n5: 當示威者當中的先頭部隊全軍覆沒，後面的市民就潰不成軍。此時，警察就一鼓作氣，連翻進攻，令後排和平示威的市民也失去根據地，警方清場完成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190616/59719041?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190616%2F59719041%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhn5V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=b4034d53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190616%2F59719041%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=168163c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190616/59719041?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"efd4da29d726b13c1f0aed3705182c1cb521dccb","tid":1229598,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"有冇其他戰役一看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b48af1da9dae81254e7cc1c178b5172f45999f","tid":1229598,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"人 向前衝防線= 人嘅密度低咗=易攻咗"}]}